#### Time

```js
console.log(new Intl.DateTimeFormat('default', {
  hour: 'numeric',
  minute: 'numeric',
  second: 'numeric'
}).format(date))
// → '2:00:00 pm'
```

#### Date

```js
console.log(new Intl.DateTimeFormat('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'numeric',
  day: 'numeric'
}).format(date))
// → '12/19/2012'
```

To specify options without a locale, use `'default'` as a locale.
